  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a multicenter, randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled trial involving subjects
      with NASH cirrhosis and severe portal hypertension (defined as HVPG ≥12 mmHg as determined
      by the central reader assigned to this study). Upon successful screening, subjects will be
      randomized to receive either emricasan 50 mg BID, 25 mg BID, or 5 mg BID or matching placebo
      BID.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
